:

*Mačka je spavala pod kaučem.* (The cat was sleeping under the couch.)

*Mačka je mjaukala u slavu novog domaćina.* (The cat meowed in honor of the new host.)

*Mačka je uspjela da se popne na najvišu policu u sobi.* (The cat managed to climb up to the highest shelf in the room.)

*Mačke su se igrali u dvorištu.* (The cats were playing in the yard.)

*Mačić je ljubazno dočekan od starijih mačaka.* (The kitten was warmly welcomed by the older cats.)

*Mačke su bile sretne što je njihov vlasnik došao kući.* (The cats were happy that their owner came home.)